Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遺跡的位置已經知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就花點時間好好找一下不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太浪費時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然無法詳細說明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之不快點過掉的話就糟糕了
