Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你了 要我幹什麼都行 給我提示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要通關就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以哦 給你提示
